@EarthRangerTech @SkylightMarine uses satellite imagery &amp; millions of daily vessel signals to surface potential illegal fishing in near real time.

This year Argentina used it to identify and fine a vessel without boarding it. 

We’re also working with @SkyTruth on pollution data. https://t.co/DE4dtjLFZJ

